MM5D Growing house controlling and remote monitoring system
===========================================================

I. General information
----------------------

  It is an internal software for MM5D Raspberry Pi based controlling and
monitoring equipment. It measures internal and external temperature (or gets
it from another MM5D) and internal humidity, checks four programmable inputs,
switch outputs, error lights and three colours light tower. You can view
actual status with a browser application and administrate it with SSH client.

II. Requirements
----------------
  Hardware: Raspberry Pi 3 Model B
  Software: Raspbian Stretch Lite operation system,
            Apache webserver,
            Perl,
            Python.

III. Installation and settings
------------------------------
  Installer package is mm5d-sw-0.1-noarch.tar.gz
  See INSTALL for detailed information.

